create_time.description: Timestamp when the sitemap was created.

data_store_id.description: The unique id of the data store.

location.description: The geographic location where the data store should reside. The value can only be one of "global", "us" and "eu".

name.description: The unique full resource name of the sitemap. Values are of the format 'projects/{project}/locations/{location}/collections/{collection_id}/dataStores/{data_store_id}/siteSearchEngine/sitemaps/{sitemap_id}'. This field must be a UTF-8 encoded string with a length limit of 1024 characters.

sitemap_id.description: The unique id of the sitemap.

uri.description: Public URI for the sitemap, e.g. "www.example.com/sitemap.xml".
